import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Blogs from './Blogs'
import App from '../App.'

export default function Routes() {
  return (
    <Router>
        <switch>
            <Route path='/Blog'>
                <Blogs/>
            </Route>
            <Route path='/Home'>
                <App/>
            </Route>
        </switch>
    </Router>
    )
}
